data.description:
Seller has an Assumable VA Loan @ 4.875% SOUTH OF I-10 - Conveniently located for your commute to base, or just a quick hop onto I-10. This beautifully designed home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, plus a flex room that can be used as an office, den, or formal dining, which is perfect for anyone wanting a little extra space. An open concept floorplan that provides a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen and is ideal for both family gatherings and/or entertaining friends. There is so much pride in ownership of this home as the current owners have replaced all the carpets in the bedrooms and installed brand new LVP flooring in the main living areas. 

The master bedroom is located on the opposite side of the home as the other two large bedrooms and the master bathroom includes double sinks and has 2 closets to accommodate everyone. 

When you step into the backyard, you'll love how private it is and enjoy having a cup of coffee or glass of wine hanging by the firepit and this space is perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing at the end of your day.

Roof is 2021. Hot water 2012. HVAC 2011. 

Book a showing and see for yourself all this home as to offer.
